1. "On je bio *miran* čovek." (He was a peaceful man.)
2. "U njegovom domu vladala je *mirna* atmosfera." (A peaceful atmosphere prevailed in his home.)
3. "Postojala je *mirna* tišina u sobi." (There was a peaceful silence in the room.)
4. "Njegov ton je bio *miran* i smiren." (His tone was peaceful and calm.)
5. "Njegov stav je bio *miran* i prihvatljiv." (His attitude was peaceful and acceptable.)
6. "Njegova poruka je bila da živimo u *miru*." (His message was to live in peace.)